Awards Taylor Has Won

Since the beginning of her career, Taylor Swift has been nominated for over 500 awards, and has won 324.

The Grammy Awards
Taylor has won 10 Grammy Awards
Taylor won her 1st Album of the Year Grammy for her album "Fearless" at only 20 years old, making her the youngest winner of this award in history.
Taylor won the Grammy for Album of the Year again for her album "1989", making her the first woman to win this award twice.
Taylor's Album of the Year Acceptance Speech for "1989"



Academy of Country Music Awards
Over Taylor's career she has won 8 ACM awards, from 29 nominations.


American Music Awards
Taylor has received 23 American Music Awards, making her the most awarded female artist in AMA history


Billboard Music Awards
Taylor has received 23 awards, holding the record of most Billboard Music Awards


iHeart Radio Music Awards
Taylor has won 10 awards, making her the second most awarded artist ever, and the most awarded female in the show's history.


BMI Awards
Taylor has won 68 BMI awards. These award honor songwriters in various genres.


Source: https://taylorswift.fandom.com/wiki/List_of_awards_and_nominations_received_by_Taylor_Swift
